&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;üéµ Collaborative Rhythm Game with hand-clapping, exploring the healing power of music and interaction&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;project-overview-2&#34;&gt;Project Overview
